uide\"}, {\"begin\": 1263, \"end\": 1276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LVMH\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mo\\u00ebt Hennessy\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LVMH\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LVMH\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pharrell Williams raved about the event at the start of the month saying how the Olympics connected nations across the world.\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1279, \"end\": 1296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pharrell_Williams\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pharrell Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pharrell_Williams\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pharrell_Williams\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's an honour for me to co-host this very special event with Anna, Mr Arnault, and Brian the night before the momentous Opening Ceremony,\\\" he toldVogue.\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1560, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1469, \"end\": 1473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_of_Russia\", \"score\": 0.642239750479417, \"rank\": 0.5431858081908135, \"text\": \"Anna\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_of_Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_of_Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 1528, \"end\": 1544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics_opening_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.6161680928251053, \"rank\": 0.6116620366024391, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics_opening_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics_opening_ceremony\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Olympics are a celebration of diversity, humanity, and creativity - all of which bring us closer together as one human race.\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1691, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics are a humbling reminder that there is so much more that unites us than divides us.\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1787, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is so much beauty in sport, and we will be celebrating this joyous time in a very special way.\\\"\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1889, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"LeBron James, Lindsey Vonn and Novak Djokovic.Picture:Victor Boyko/Getty Images for LVMH x Vogue x  Charlize Theron.Picture:Julien M. Hekimian/Getty Images for LVMH x Vogue x  Elizabeth Banks.Picture:Julien M. Hekimian/Getty Images for LVMH x Vogue x  Ian Thorpe.Picture:Pascal Le Segretain/Getty Images  Jelena Djokovic and Novak Djokovic.Picture:Arnold Jerocki/Getty Images for LVMH x Vogue x  Baz Luhrman and Novak Djokovic.Picture:Victor Boyko/Getty Images for LVMH x Vogue x\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 2370, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1891, \"end\": 1903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LeBron James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}, {\"begin\": 1905, \"end\": 1917, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lindsey_Vonn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lindsey Vonn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4270517\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lindsey_Vonn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lindsey_Vonn\"}, {\"begin\": 1945, \"end\": 1951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RCA_Records\", \"score\": 0.9997043200346807, \"rank\": 0.00029540972036990343, \"text\": \"Victor\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q18127\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RCA_Records\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RCA_Records\"}, {\"begin\": 1952, \"end\": 1957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/reso